# Resort Example (`resort-example`)

> **Maintenance**: Keep this file in sync when blocks, templates, mock pages, navigation, or integrations change (`rules-sync.mdc`).

Mountain hotel / resort demo (Kope). Locales: `en` (default), `de`, `sl`. Adapter: `mock` ‚Üí Strapi later.

**Mock data folder** is `src/core/mock-data.ts/resort/` (not `resort-example`).

## Render pipeline

```
page JSON ‚Üí MockAdapter.getPage ‚Üí page.tsx
  ‚Üí resolveTemplate(page.template) ‚Üí tenant template
  ‚Üí BlockRenderer ‚Üí tenant + shared blocks
```

- **Config**: `src/tenants/resort-example/config.ts`
- **Registration**: `src/tenants/resort-example/blocks/index.ts`
- **Mock pages**: `src/core/mock-data.ts/resort/pages/*.json`

## Templates (`src/tenants/resort-example/templates/`)

| Template | Chrome | Use |
|----------|--------|-----|
| `default` | Header + footer | Home, about, contact, rooms list, room detail (current JSON) |
| `detail` | Header + footer + **main/sidebar grid** | Use when page needs two-column shell (`"template": "detail"`) |
